HEADWORD: Entitative
<hw>En"ti*ta*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Entity</er>.]</ety> <def>Considered as pure entity; abstracted from
all circumstances.</def> <au>Ellis.</au> --
